reviews.reviewText: A gender-neutral toiletry bag that's great for short trips. Can fit a lot of items, I personally use mine for dental and eyelash products when I'm traveling. The fabric is pretty thick, contributing to its overall sturdiness. Can make a great gift, too!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great traveling toiletry bag option
reviews.reviewText: Off the bat, material feels pretty decent quality and durable to the touch. I ordered a Navy one, but it's more of an in-between shade of blue and gray. Stitching is clean and the bag expands a fair amount (though obviously more = bigger). Waterproof sectioning is lined with some heavy-ish plastic, and main compartment has lots of elastic partitions for keeping your bottles sorted. Carry handle is an added bonus.
